{
  "abstract": "The world collection of pigeonpea germplasm maintained at ICRISAT has only 12 accessions from Indonesia. The crop has been under cultivation in the islands of Indonesia for the last several centuries. Therefore, Indonesia was identified as one of the priority regions for pigeonpea germplasm collection.",
